My favorite recipe YET! 🍪🥛 Cookies & Cream (protein) NICE CREAM! Fluffiness level 📈 try this ASAP!

3 frozen bananas
6 coconut milk ice cubes
1 teaspoon cacao powder
1 scoop @bloomsupps cookies & cream protein
Dash of milk
Blend!
Add cookie crumbles
Freeze for 1 hour

DELISH! 😋
